### Manual Testing Instructions
1.  Load the extension in Chrome/Firefox (Developer Mode).
2.  Open a website with media (e.g., a test HLS stream).
3.  Open the extension popup.
4.  Verify that resources appear in the list.
5.  Go to Settings -> Capture.
6.  Test disabling 'Capture Video' and refresh the page. Verify video resources are NOT captured.
